w is that not just basic humanity, should not matter if you dont have a place of your own or you have 12.  like really wtf does dick cheney do when he sharts his suit in a limo, they dont have bathrooms or showers, wouldn&amp;#39;t it just be utterly decent to have common public places to get your dignity back? and as for people &amp;#39;helping&amp;#39; totally, wtf? want to help someone? start by talking to them, hell my massive stress is lightened when a stranger gives me the decency of just opening up a conversation. we need to learn how to be human again, we all have problems and homelessness is a symptom of a problem, it isn&amp;#39;t the problem. and for people that don&amp;#39;t get that, are aboriginal people homeless? chew on that a bit for some perspective.</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/7696518298356395703/comments/default/8242719796679227427'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/7696518298356395703/comments/default/8242719796679227427'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2011/04/how-to-solve-homelessness.html?showComment=1374102194139#c8242719796679227427' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2011/04/how-to-solve-homelessness.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-7696518298356395703' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/posts/default/7696518298356395703' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-535359399"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="4:03 PM"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-4015207197428440573</id><pub