ss.  That&amp;#39;s just another form of rejection and prejudice. You&amp;#39;re right that economic justice is important, though, it would probably make surviving homeless easier. However as long as the prejudice against homelessness remains, it will probably always be harder to be homeless than it has to be.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;P.S. It&amp;#39;s unfortunate that homelessness isn&amp;#39;t respected as much as mountain climbing.  They both appear to me to be admirable tests of human courage, except no mountaineer ever got spit on.</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/7696518298356395703/comments/default/8224621243970214370'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/7696518298356395703/comments/default/8224621243970214370'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2011/04/how-to-solve-homelessness.html?showComment=1322437568488#c8224621243970214370' title=''/><author><name>Zella</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2011/04/how-to-solve-homelessness.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-7696518298356395703' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/posts/default/7696518298356395703' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1953513788"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="3:46 PM"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-976881579608460692</id><published>2011-10-02T23:45:27.767-07:00</published><updated>2011-10-02T23:45:27.767-07:00</updated><title type='text'>Homelessness is an economical problem and a mental...</title><content type='html'>Homelessness i